data.description: Looking for a house with no carpet?? THIS IS THE ONE!! Everything in this home, inside and out, has been so well done! The floors were installed in 2016, look like brand new!! This  home has had several updates such as new appliances, new floors, a large extended deck with an above ground pool, and a 16 x 20 ft storage building that has been finished out, just needs electricity run to it! This home has a spacious living room with an eat in area and extra built in storage. The stairs are hardwood, and the large dining room could be used as an office, or set up as an additional bedroom. The electric fireplace in the den isn't attached, but will stay. It's a perfect finish to this family room! Did I mention the partial wrap around porch that's just perfect for sitting and reading, sipping some sweet tea, or visiting with friends and family! This home is truly move in ready and waiting for you! Don't miss out on this hidden treasure! Schedule your appointment today!
